1. 16 primary colors (color name):

body{

color:green;

background-color:pink;

}

1. RGB values:

body{

color:green;

background-color:rgb(240,28,235);

}

3. Hex codes:

body{

color:green;

background-color:#ff9999;

}



Notes:
color points to words in body tag will be shown in green.
background-color points to the web background color will be shown in lime.
